data.description: Welcome home to Berlin Plank Road! Quietly located in Somerset Township approximately miles out of town.  This charming cape cod style home has much to offer.  With a spacious living room and separate dining room awaiting gatherings!  You will have no trouble at preparing these upcoming dinners in the large kitchen. From your morning coffee to a relaxing evening, picture yourself sitting on your deck located inside your private fenced in yard.  Or maybe you prefer to take your cuppa and toast marshmallows around the fire pit. Did I mention the raised garden? With just under an acre, this property is large enough to enjoy and a breeze to maintain.  Several updates and upgrades have been made including new flooring in kitchen, new bedroom doors with updated hardware and new trim upstairs. This property comes with expansive potential! Sellers are motivated and ready to consider your offer!
